high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, once at the wall turn left and walk up to the round black table.
Pick up the metal knife off of the round black table.
Slice up the head of lettuce that is on the round black table.
Turn left and begin walking to the oven, then hang a right and walk up to the section of counter with the coffee machine on it.
Place the metal knife in the green can below the kitchen counter where the coffee machine is.
Turn around and walk back to where the head of lettuce is on the round black table.
Pick up a piece of sliced lettuce.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and continue over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the piece of sliced lettuce onto the metal pan inside the fridge.
Remove the metal pan with the piece of sliced lettuce on it from the fridge and close the door.
Turn right, take a step then turn right again and walk across the room, once at the wall turn left and walk up to the round black table.
Place the metal pan with a piece of sliced lettuce on it onto the round black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a metal pan with a piece of sliced lettuce in it onto the round black table.

high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the counter, then turn left to face the black table.
Pick the knife up from off of the table.
Slice the lettuce on the table with the knife.
Move to the left to face the coffee machine on the counter.
Place the knife in the green bucket below the counter top.
Move to the right to face the black table.
Pick up a slice of the lettuce from the table.
Turn around and go to the right to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the lettuce inside on a plate.
Remove the plate with the lettuce on it and shut the refrigerator door.
Turn around and go to the left to face the black table.
Place the plate with the lettuce on top of the black table.
anns.task_desc: Set the lettuce that's on the plate on top of the black table.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the table.
Pick up the butter knife on the table.
Slice the lettuce into pieces.
Walk to the trash bin under the coffee maker.
Throw the butter knife in the trash bin.
Walk back over to the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Walk across the room to the fridge.
Put the lettuce on the cold plate inside the fridge.
Take the cold plate with lettuce on it out of the fridge.
Take the cold plate with lettuce on it across the room to the table.
Set the cold plate with lettuce down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate with lettuce on it onto the table.
